      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="Y49-657Y">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-Y49-657Y-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y49-657Y-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y49-657Y-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">The following Epitaph was written with Chalk upon a Tombstone in the Close of Salisbury when D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Burnet filled that See. It was strongly suspected &amp; reported that Dean Swift was the Author &amp; had taken a long Journey and uncommon Pains to publish his Satire &amp; conceal the Author.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-Y49-657Y-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y49-657Y-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y49-657Y-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Y49-657Y-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y49-657Y-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y49-657Y-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-1" n="1">Here Sarum lies, who was as wise</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-2" n="2">and learned as Tom Aquinas.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-3" n="3">Lawn Sleeves he wore, yet was no more</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-4" n="4">A Christian than Socinus.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-5" n="5"><lb/>Oaths pro &amp; con he swallow'd down</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-6" n="6">Lov'd Gold like any layman;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-7" n="7">He preach'd &amp; pray'd &amp; yet betray'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-8" n="8">God's holy Church for Mammon.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-9" n="9">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-10" n="10">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-11" n="11">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-12" n="12">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-13" n="13"><lb/>If such a Soul, to heaven Stole</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-14" n="14">And pass'd the Devil's Clutches</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-15" n="15">I do presume, there may be Room</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-657Y-line-16" n="16">For Marlbro' &amp; his Dutchess.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
